				<td colspan="2"><span>I searched the forum I think this subject wasn't discussed before, if it had please pardon me. I am sure this should be quite a hot topic.
<br />

<br />
Basically which one is better? or are they so similiar its hard to compare?
<br />

<br />
I don't know which one I should be going for, but I am sort of a fashion freak probably want to wear the full suit if possible and if you consider all the ups and downs which one would you do? And if a mix is really better I would like to hear somethinig about it.
<br />

<br />
Just some things I am considering when deciding which:
<br />
-EP flagged (not time though) so you can get EP armor (but you have to out bid other people so it will take a while to wear the whole thing or anything)
<br />

<br />
-Augs, this is the BIG thing, EP doesn't have slot 3 or 2 and neither does a lot of other armor that is not from ldon
<br />

<br />
Just for the sake of arguement lets not go into how long its gonna take for you to get enough points to get the armor compare to raiding EP to get it. Just want to know which one is better with all the augs and stats compared.
<br />
</span></td>
