				<td colspan="2"><span>Personally, I would go for a mixture of the two things, that is if you have the time to do LDoN.  I would go with LDoN bracers over EP bracers because even though you will not get the same stats out of them, you will also save valuable points that you will want for the good bracers(once you get to time you're gonna want to have the points advantage).  I would highly recommend getting EP Arms/Boots/Helm/Gloves, and legs are so rare off EP gods that you shouldn't even think about getting them until Time, so I would probably go with LDoN there.  You cannot get a full set of Rizlona's until you are far into time, so for aesthetic purposes full Rizlona's is rather impractical.</span></td>
